KEGG pathways

Source: R/GetPriorKnowledge.R
metsigdb_kegg.Rd

KEGG pathways

Usage

metsigdb_kegg()

Value

A data frame containing the KEGG pathways suitable for ORA.

Examples

metsigdb_kegg()
